# Tree Folder

This folder contains the core structure of the deterministic reflection system.

## Files

* `reflection-tree.tsv`
  The main decision tree represented as structured data.
  Each row defines a node, including questions, decisions, reflections, and transitions.

* `tree-diagram.md`
  A visual representation of the decision tree using a Mermaid flowchart.

## Purpose

This folder represents the **actual product logic** — a fully deterministic tree that guides user reflection without any AI at runtime.
